{"tid":2036113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何鴻燊的港澳國際線】何鴻燊二十年前的美夢，是將香港租予聯合國托管。","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T12:39:11.000Z","uid":117837,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"87e097a9c71400cf710f5d721ebbae337a055042","tid":2036113,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"【何鴻燊的港澳國際線】#國際線前輩 1989年六四事件發生後，何鴻燊在7月於港澳兩地報章發表《美夢成真》一文，倡議中國收回香港與澳門後，出租予聯合國100年，以作為聯合國總部，並稱港澳將進入「一個空前未有的繁華境界」。今天何生蒙主感召，我們只能透過他的事蹟及文章才見到他的智慧。<br />\n<br />\n何鴻燊《美夢成真》(1989年7月28日）原文：<br />\n<br />\n//一九九七年，仲夏的一個黃昏吧&hellip;英國國旗徐徐地下降了&hellip;五星紅旗冉冉升起&hellip;我揉揉眼睛&hellip;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>遠處添馬艦總部，除五星紅旗外，還有許多其它國家的旗幟：美國、英國、葡萄牙、澳洲、法國、意大利、德國，一時難以分辨&hellip;</strong></span>市民傾城而出，奔走相告，額手稱慶&hellip;夢境一轉，彷彿到一九八九年十月一日，看見北京天安門城樓上&hellip;鄧小平先生莊嚴宣佈：「中國一定要實現四個現代化&hellip;為港澳的經濟繁華持續發展，為恢復海外人士對中國的信心，為提高中國的國際地位及聲望，更為開拓世界持久和平的偉大事業，我藉著四十周年國慶吉日，在退休前特送給港澳同胞一份大禮&hellip;希望大家不要老是記著秋後算賬。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>在香港、澳門回歸中國時，將兩地租與聯合國一百年，以便在港澳設立聯合國總部。</strong></span>」這真是天籟的福音&hellip;//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/100696664_2444593735815737_8809475487467307008_o.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=hqKrW0U1lnYAX-MFGg3&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=9dff7bafa81853556275e6646c6859b0&amp;oe=5EF2C25E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F100696664_2444593735815737_8809475487467307008_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DhqKrW0U1lnYAX-MFGg3%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D9dff7bafa81853556275e6646c6859b0%26oe%3D5EF2C25E&h=1431c818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fccthinktank/photos/a.1384494598492328/2444593729149071/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffccthinktank%2Fphotos%2Fa.1384494598492328%2F2444593729149071%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=bb4e1cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fccthinktank/photos/a.1384494598492328/2444593729149071/</a>"},{"pid":"cc80ec7b7f9e2520df164c521a2be153797ed8bc","tid":2036113,"uid":117837,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"何生真係有遠見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f069258d66fd3995c6b55e872a3ff4cd389f049d","tid":2036113,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1abd9826d1ea9d3a3ea306ac20c9e5bf2d7661c","tid":2036113,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0383346858a8dba334a6c78eab282da3f87a443","tid":2036113,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"何生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cea86754e1e1506c19f9ae5759062d63b524ffc","tid":2036113,"uid":117837,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/99111957_10157549490643845_5873038675410944000_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=1480c5&amp;_nc_ohc=w8IOFlzSZ1QAX9DL97k&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=b5b546761a194474da8ba0d4a16554c3&amp;oe=5EF164B8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net